  "summary": "Main\nThe Baltic Dry index retreated on Tuesday, following two sessions of gains. Weak cargo ordering activities in the capesize and panamax segments caused the headline index to retreat by nearly three per cent. Easing tensions in the Middle East contributed to losses for energy commodities while receding optimism over the Chinese economy weighed on iron ore and base metals.",
